ave full control over their account. Users are the full and sole owner of their exchange accounts and carry all responsibilities that come with opening, holding, and managing such accounts.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">2.2 Asset allocation<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">Capital Easy Finance uses dynamic, proprietary algorithms to define and perform portfolio allocation, based on user input. Manual trades or transactions conducted by users may limit Capital Easy Finance\u2019s account monitoring and reporting ability.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">2.3 Fund deposits and withdrawals<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">Users are responsible for depositing and withdrawing funds to\/from their account, however Capital Easy Finance will provide clear instructions on how to do so.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">2.4 Account monitoring and reporting<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">Capital Easy Finance will continuously monitor user accounts and provide users with a monthly dashboard with easy-to-understand portfolio and performance details.<\/span><\/p><h3><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\"><b>3. Fees<\/b><\/span><\/h3><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">3.1 Fee structure<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">Capital Easy Finance offers different plans: freemium, and performance fee. The freemium plan is totally free and offers limited functionality.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">Our customers especially like the no-profit-no-pay model as it means that Capital Easy Finance only gets paid if the customer wins. We like this also!<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">3.2 Promotions<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">Capital Easy Finance reserves the right to apply promotional discounts to the fees listed under 3.1. This is completely at Capital Easy Finance\u2019s discretion.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">3.3 Other fees<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">Capital Easy Finance does not charge any additional or hidden fees. For any transaction or trading fees that may be charged by cryptocurrency exchanges and\/or banks, users accept full responsibility.<\/span><\/p><h3><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\"><b>4. Security<\/b><\/span><\/h3><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">4.1 Infrastructure<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">Capital Easy Finance is powered by Google Cloud. Google Cloud helps reducing the cost, complexity, and risk associated with security and compliance in the cloud.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">4.2 Exchanges<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">Capital Easy Finance thoroughly vets its partners and only works with major \u201ctop-10\u201d exchanges. User funds remain on their personal exchange account and interactions between Capital Easy Finance and user accounts are performed by means of customer owned API keys. API access is limited, hence in the unlikely event of a security breach, no fund withdrawal can take place.<\/span><\/p><h3><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\"><b>5. Disclaimer<\/b><\/span><\/h3><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">5.1 Financial advice<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">Capital Easy Finance does not provide financial advice. Capital Easy Finance is not a Registered Investment Advisor, Broker\/Dealer, Financial Analyst, Bank, Securities Broker, Commodity Trade Advisor, or Financial Planner. The information provided, such as optimal fund allocation, is based on user input and for information purposes only. The Information is not intended to be and does not constitute financial advice or any other advice, is general in nature and not specific to you. Before using Capital Easy Finance, users should seek the advice of a qualified investment professional and undertake their own due diligence. Capital Easy Finance is not responsible for any investment decision made by users.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">5.2 Warranties<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">Capital Easy Finance disclaims to the full extent authorized by law any and all warranties, whether express or implied, including, without limitation, any implied warranties, merchantability or fitness for a particular purpose. Capital Easy Finance does not warrant that its services and applications will be free of bugs, errors, viruses or other defects, nor that trade results will be profitable.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">5.3 Liability<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">In no event can Capital Easy Finance or any of its owners be liable to users or any party related to users for any indirect, incidental, consequential, special, exemplary, or punitive damages, lost profits, or losses, even if Capital Easy Finance has been advised of the possibility of such damages. In any event, Capital Easy Finance\u2019s total aggregate liability to users for all damages of every kind and type (regardless of whether based in contract or tort) shall not exceed the fees paid to Capital Easy Finance for the use of our services or applications.<\/span><\/p><h3><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\"><b>6. Risks<\/b><\/span><\/h3><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">Investing in any asset class, including crypto currencies, holds numerous risks, for example: technology risks, exchange risks, security risks, regulatory risks.\u00a0 Before deciding to leverage Capital Easy Finance services, users should carefully consider their investment objectives and risk appetite. The possibility exists that users lose some or all of their initial investment and therefore no money should be invested that users cannot afford to lose.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">As with any market, for a transaction to happen it requires a seller, a buyer, and a price agreement. Loss-limiting strategies such as stop-loss orders may not be effective because market conditions or technological issues may make it impossible to execute stop-loss orders. Capital Easy Finance is not responsible for any losses incurred as a result of using Capital Easy Finance\u2019s advisory services.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">\u200d<\/span><\/p><h3><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\"><b>7. Privacy<\/b><\/span><\/h3><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">Capital Easy Finance is fully compliant with GDPR (General Data Protection Regulation), an EU regulation enforceable as of May 25, 2018. Capital Easy Finance stores the minimum possible amount of user data necessary to deliver its services. Stored user data includes: name, date of birth, country of residence, email address, and exchange API keys (encrypted). User data will never be shared with any third party before explicit user consent. Users have the right for their user data to be forgotten, which can be requested over email.<\/span><\/p><h3><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\"><b>8. Communication<\/b><\/span><\/h3><p><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">The User understands and agrees to the preceding sections. The User also agrees to the following:<\/span><\/p><ul><li aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">User agrees to not hold Capital Easy Finance liable for any realized trading loss in any currency or asset;<\/span><\/li><li aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">User reserves the right to stop using Capital Easy Finance at any point;<\/span><\/li><li aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">You agrees and warrants that any information provided to Capital Easy Finance is accurate and complete;<\/span><\/li><li aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">User agrees that Capital Easy Finance is offering a Software as a Service (SaaS). This means that Capital Easy Finance monitors user accounts on users\u2019 behalf on exchanges that are not affiliated with Capital Easy Finance;<\/span><\/li><li aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"color: #f0f0f0;\">User agrees to take full responsibility for id